snippet.title: Myth Caller: The Nightmare Shaman -- Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
[this video shows outdated gameplay from 2021]

Myth Caller: The Nightmare Shaman is a 3D collectathon platformer where you catch monsters, fuse them together, and fight in real-time combat!

Now in full-scale development.

Song:
The Vikings by Alexander Nakarada | https://www.serpentsoundstudios.com
Music promoted by https://www.free-stock-music.com
